Sentry - Advanced Sprite Editor
----------------------------------

-----> Version 0.0.2
C++ Builder 11 port

-----> Version 0.0.1

* History
This tool was coded in spring of 2007 to replace the various custom sprite tools
used by the Lethal Metal and Pure Power Tactical Engine and several other
internal projects. The goal is to provide a common sprite platform that will
be able to support a large variety of projects, from mobile device to PC.

